::The Oblitertrons::

Dark One stops as he sees two bots on the ground, recognizing them as the 
bots Zardus had ordered to kill. One of them was the Maximal hostage from 
before (Tavatron), the other a tough looking warrior (Dinobot).

"There they are," he says into his comm to the other Oblitercons, "Kill them."

With that, he dips downward, firing laser shots through the trees at the two 
Maximals.

Pyro transforms into tank mode, driving through the forest toward Dinobot and 
Tavatron, scorching trees on his way. The rest of the Oblitercons run behind, 
ready to tear the Maximals to shreds.
